ba49ac6d-ceff-4a9d-b3b1-7b89afdd88cc"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/f9deda41-78ef-4596-a80f-59f61a879682.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7 5p Progress Report — AHV Works] You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV Works ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 15th, 2026 - 4:42 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-15 04:42 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776228154414,"__openclaw":{"id":"4a09e21a","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the sessions list and compare against the last known state in memory/heartbeat-state.json."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_994rjtsh4bxr_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"messageLimit":2}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_994rjtsh4bxr_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":438,"output":102,"totalTokens":14484,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776228154556,"responseId":"062e4a3bd1c37a64fe0bb3d20810d546","__openclaw":{"id":"9686b231","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"label":"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776227955466,"sessionId":"33d839d6-ce6c-4696-9bd6-5ca0180fedd6","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44600,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776199558073,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/33d839d6-ce6c-4696-9bd6-5ca0180fedd6.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The memory search returned no results - the heartbeat-state.json file doesn't exist or is empty. So I have no previous state to compare against.\n\nHowever, I have enough information from the sessions_list to report the current state. Since there's no previous state, I should treat this as a fresh state and report if anything notable is happening.\n\nLet me analyze the current state (as of 04:39 UTC 15 Apr 2026):\n\n**Running sessions:**\n1. `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX 5p cron) — running ✅ (this is the current cron itself)\n\n\n2. `agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258` (QLHV group) — running ✅ (updatedAt ~04:30)\n3. `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV 5p cron) — running ✅\n4. `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813` (Agent Status to Lead) — running ✅ (updatedAt ~04:34)\n5. `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a` (Daily Briefing) — unknown status\n\n, no updatedAt timestamp (likely orphaned)\n6. `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ac986a8d` — running but stale (updated ~11h ago)\n7. `agent:master-orchestrator:cron:b653a6c0` — orphan (updated ~14h ago)\n\nMost sessions have finished — the main agent, telegram:direct, the group, and various others are all done. I'm seeing a mix of running and completed tasks across the agent ecosystem, with the core orchestrator sessions still active while many child tasks have wrapped up.\n\nThe DTLX group cron has been idle for over 15 hours, so it's probably stuck or orphaned. Looking at the changes since the last report from the Telegram group session, the Lead direct session ended cleanly around 04:34 UTC after completing the ahv-openclaw-setup work. The QLHV 5p cron is still running normally, and the three planner subagents spawned from it have all finished. The DTLX 5p cron is also stable with no new failures, though there are a couple of orphaned cron jobs that have been stuck for over 30 hours.\n\nComparing the current state at 04:39 UTC to the last known state at 04:34 UTC, everything appears stable — all three cron monitors are still running without issues, no new failures, and no changes to report. I'm doing a broader check across the system to see if there's anything else happening, but I'm finding mostly completed sessions with no active work underway. Looking at the DTLX 5p cron session specifically, it has the current cron running plus an Agent Status monitor and QLHV 5p cron both running, with the Lead direct session ended, so I need to dig deeper into what's actually active in the current window.\n\nComparing the two cycles at 04:37 and 04:39, the session counts are identical and all the same cron jobs are running — nothing has changed. Since there's no previous heartbeat state file to compare against, I should treat this as a fresh snapshot, but the real question is whether anything new has occurred since the last report. The previous cycle reported that the Lead direct session ended cleanly and the QLHV 5p planner subagents finished, both of which are already in the current state, so there's still nothing new to report.\n\nI'm also noticing the DTLX 5p cron session at 04:39 shows zero active child sessions — those three subagents that were running at 04:37 have all completed by now. And the QLHV group session has been idle since 04:30, so it hasn't received any new reports in the last cycle. This pattern of completed subagents and idle sessions is consistent across both cycles, so there's genuinely nothing new to flag.\n\nI'm realizing I don't have a stored previous state to compare against anyway — the heartbeat state was empty — so I should stay silent and wait for the next cycle to see if anything changes."},{"type":"text","text":"No changes detected since the last report (04:37 UTC). All 3 cron monitors stable, no new failures, Lead direct already reported as ended. State matches previous cycle. Staying silent."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":30249,"output":905,"totalTokens":45505,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":407,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776227995437,"responseId":"062e499d98fb8497560052351f6de990","__openclaw":{"id":"07a8e325","seq":5}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258","kind":"group","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:-5163901258","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776227831146,"sessionId":"8e0cb2bc-8245-4c89-bc2c-e3cca2257d0f","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":108109,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776163408296,"endedAt":1776163783190,"runtimeMs":8014,"childSessions":["agent:senior-backend:subagent:f42cdd0e-8c76-42e7-ac2a-f1474568e0d4","agent:senior-frontend:subagent:cf1f74df-fd21-47ed-8a91-4c146aead234","agent:ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:469f1534-e128-44ea-af0d-73710c607372","agent:ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:ae038bd3-76fe-45b5-a5d7-b8797a299b2d"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:-5163901258","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/8e0cb2bc-8245-4c89-bc2c-e3cca2257d0f.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | 04:34 UTC 15 Apr\n\nChanges detected:\n• 💬 Lead direct (telegram:direct:6053576134) — ENDED cleanly at ~04:34 UTC, completed ahv-openclaw-setup repo structure + SSH key delivery\n• ✅ 3 cron sessions stable — DTLX 5p, QLHV 5p, Agent Status all running normally\n\nPipeline: HEALTHY ✅\n• Active sessions: 3 (DTLX 5p ✅ QLHV 5p ✅ Agent Status ✅)\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Blockers: cron:ac986a8d orphan (~37h) | cron:b653a6c0 orphan (~32h) — low priority\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"timestamp":1776227819827,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","sourceChannel":"telegram","sourceTool":"sessions_send"},"__openclaw":{"id":"d35f990e","seq":1239}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Skip."},{"type":"text","text":"\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":290,"output":11,"totalTokens":108120,"cacheRead":7778,"cacheWrite":100041,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776227819999,"responseId":"062e48ee9b3d6d7bbffbd45a36c48855","__openclaw":{"id":"5e571c55","seq":1240}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:main","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-main","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat","to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1776227394727,"sessionId":"bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd52